=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Tutorials_06-Presented-in-Living-Stereo_ex5 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 221 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 220.6358
  harmonic_decay_rate: -8.9521
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1227
  pitch_clarity: 98.3039
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -9.3082
  resonance_freq: 538.3301

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
